cessdate=11 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Preki}}\n* [http://www.ussoccerplayers.com/players/preki/ Preki profile at United States National Soccer Players]\n* [http://www.nasljerseys.com/MISL/Players/P/Preki.htm MISL stats]\n* {{NFT player|id=11454}}\n\n{{Seattle Sounders FC squad}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n| title       = United States squads\n| bg          = white\n| fg          = #002868\n| bordercolor = #BF0A30\n| list1 =\n{{United States squad 1998 CONCACAF Gold Cup}}\n{{United States squad 1998 FIFA World Cup}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n|title=Awards\n|bg=gold\n|fg=navy\n|list1=\n{{MLS All-Star Game MVP}}\n{{Major League Soccer MVP Award}}\n{{2003 MLS Best XI}}\n{{MLS Coach of the Year}}\n{{MLSXI}}\n{{National Soccer Hall of Fame members}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title = Managerial positions\n|list1 =\n{{Chivas USA managers}}\n{{Toronto FC managers}}\n{{Saint Louis FC coaches}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Preki}}\n[[Category:1963 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American people of Serbian descent]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Belgrade]]\n[[Category:Yugoslav emigrants to the United States]]\n[[Category:Yugoslav footballers]]\n[[Category:Serbian footballers]]\n[[Category:American soccer players]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Red Star Belgrade footballers]]\n[[Category:Tacoma Stars players]]\n[[Category:St. Louis Storm players]]\n[[Category:Everton F.C. players]]\n[[Category:San Jose Grizzlies players]]\n[[Category:Portsmouth F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Sporting Kansas City players]]\n[[Category:Miami Fusion players]]\n[[Category:Yugoslav First League players]]\n[[Category:Major Indoor Soccer League (1978\u20131992) players]]\n[[Category:Premier League players]]\n[[Category:Continental Indoor Soccer League players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:Major League Soccer players]]\n[[Category:Major League Soccer All-Stars]]\n[